        <title>Pessimistic Lock</title>
        <sect2>
            <title>Pessimistic Lock Lookup</title>
            <para>The <emphasis role="bold">Pessimistic Lock Lookup</emphasis> screen lets you
                review existing locks and manually release them.</para>
            <para>You get to this screen by clicking the <emphasis role="bold">Pessimistic Lock
                    Lookup</emphasis> option on the <emphasis role="bold">Main
                Menu</emphasis>.</para>
            <figure><title>Pessimistic Lock Lookup</title>
                <mediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                        <imagedata fileref="../images/pessimistic_lock_lookup.png"/>
                    </imageobject>
                </mediaobject>
